%define appname IO-File-Cached

Summary: IO::File::Cached - On demand file caching
Name: perl-%{appname}
Version: @VERSION@
Release: 1
Copyright: GPL
Group: Applications/Internet
Source: %{appname}-%{version}.tar.gz
BuildRoot: /var/tmp/%{appname}-%{version}-root
